<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-12602] The LICENSE and NOTICE files don&apos;t list everything they should</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-12602</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jmclean&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jmclean&quot;&gt;jmclean&lt;/a&gt; raised this on the mailing list: &lt;a href=&quot;https://lists.apache.org/thread.html/r2df54c11c10d3d38443054998bc7dd92d34362641733c2fb7c579b50%40%3Cdev.kafka.apache.org%3E&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://lists.apache.org/thread.html/r2df54c11c10d3d38443054998bc7dd92d34362641733c2fb7c579b50%40%3Cdev.kafka.apache.org%3E&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We need to make&#160; the license file match what we are actually shipping in source and binary distributions.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13369142">KAFKA-12602</key>
            <summary>The LICENSE and NOTICE files don&apos;t list everything they should</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
